Designer for WiX Toolset provides developers with a set of designers to quickly configure any WiX setup projects in a familiar Visual Studio way.

With this tool, you can forget the plain WiX XML and focus solely on your deployment logic. This tool integrates its own editors with the Visual Studio IDE and offers an array of visual designers to configure the file system, registry, user interface, custom actions and launch conditions for your WiX setup projects.

All setup project types are supported including standard msi installation packages, web-deployment setup projects, merge modules, etc.